    /**
     * @dev Exponentiation (_x^_y) with unsigned 18 decimal fixed point base and exponent.
     *
     * Reverts if ln(_x) * _y is smaller than `MIN_NATURAL_EXPONENT`, or larger than `MAX_NATURAL_EXPONENT`.
     */
